Tools/parts Needed: N/A
Instructions: Pop the two metal clips separating the box and allowing access to the the air filter and pull up on the side that has the hose.
Image:
Tools/parts Needed: N/A
Instructions: Remove old air-filter.
Image:
Tools/parts Needed: New Air-filter
Instructions: Place new air filter inside box and ensure it has the same orientation as the old air filter.
Image:
Tools/parts Needed: N/A
Instructions: push the side of the separated box back down and fasten the two metal clips back together making sure the box is tight together.